{"tid":344292,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"譚芷昀Celine出戰全美一叮 評審激讚直入36強","createTime":"2017-08-02T07:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T10:09:04.000Z","uid":118455,"like":11,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b93fb3fcfcaebf6ea7598d2d80f75396b1f53e12","tid":344292,"uid":118455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/02/153614_15186dbecc2c3fad980c2d7329a0e56f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F02%2F153614_15186dbecc2c3fad980c2d7329a0e56f.png&h=5fc6f2d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有小巨肺之稱、年僅9歲的譚芷昀（Celine Tam），在香港時間今早最新一集的美國選秀節目《全美一叮》（America's Got Talent）再度登場。<br />\n<br />\nCeline在最新一集獻唱Michael Boton的歌曲《How Am I Supposed to Live Without You》，繼續以無比自信和強勁唱功，獲得今集客串評審Laverne Cox按下Golden Buzzer，直接進入36強淘汰賽！<br />\n<br />\n從官方影片所見，當評審按下下Golden Buzzer時，Celine顯得相當震驚，興奮得說不出話來，最後評審走上台和Celine擁抱。<br />\n<br />\n根據網上資料，下星期會進行其他組別的淘汰賽，讓其餘參賽者爭取餘下的36強出線資格。現時36強淘汰賽已經誕生其中26位，另一位來自美國的「小巨肺」Angelica Hale，亦憑評審按下Golden Buzzer成功直入36強。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T9ZbP7Fkzug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DT9ZbP7Fkzug&d=9V8l8fa56wF2ewEMC3kAMtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=bf10f805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T9ZbP7Fkzug</a>"},{"pid":"d90d485c9108db3dd8a4daf90367d82825074439","tid":344292,"uid":118455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:39:29.000Z","msg":"中意Angelica Hale多D, 但上次揀歌好過今次"},{"pid":"94a637d4fe6cf065a65afe0de555afc05a0064d0","tid":344292,"uid":80764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8ae079c27e36e2ff59ccfd611ec4411ece6c41","tid":344292,"uid":33104